Package sk.stu.fiit.logic

Class Schedule

java.lang.Object
sk.stu.fiit.logic.Schedule
public class Schedule
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents a relation between the building and an exact employee. Also, use the Employee, Building or WeekDays classes to know even more details.
